text: Raina Giusti (born 29 May 1997) is a Maltese footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Malta women's national team. ==Career== Giusti has been capped for the Malta national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Maltese women's footballers Category:Malta women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards
